729818f-c.title: Richmond: Victory Boulevard - Speedwell Avenue
729818f-c.text:
(1)
3301 Viotory Boulevard, west side, south of
Speedwell Avenue, showing the J. VroiF ouse (Butler's
1863 map). On subsequent maps, those of 1874 and 1898;
it appears as the Vroom house. IIn 1907 and 1917 it was
oamned by D. B. Boscher (Boschen).
May 19, 1932
P. L. Sperr
(2)
The Vrohe House, looking north across the
farmland.
May 19, 1932
P. L. Sperr
(3)
The same, at a later date.
May, 19, 1935
P. L. Sperr
